:SE555 :hasDurationOf "Duration varies; may resolve after stopping the drug" .

:SE556 :hasSideEffectDescription "A reaction that causes symptoms similar to lupus, such as joint pain, muscle pain, fever, and skin rash. Symptoms usually improve when the medicine is discontinued." .
