:SP122 :hasStewardshipDescription "May be taken with or without food: May be taken during or between meals. Swallow whole, do not chew" .
:SP122 :hasReference :R010 .

:SP123 :hasReference :R010 .
:SP123 :hasStewardshipDescription "Dosage is according to doctor's instructions only" .

:SP124 :hasReference :R038 .
:SP124 :hasStewardshipDescription "Azithromycin should be taken at least one hour before or two hours after administration of food and antacid preparations" .

:SP125 :hasStewardshipDescription "May be taken with or without food; Preferably taken 2hrs after meals" .
:SP125 :hasReference :R091 .

